Depends: python3, python3-gi, gir1.2-gtk-3.0, flatpak, apt, wget, gir1.2-gdkpixbuf-2.0, gir1.2-pango-1.0
Provides: package-manager
Section: utils
Priority: optional
Homepage: https://sourceforge.net/projects/essora/
Description: Comprehensive multi-format package manager for Essora Linux
 Essora Store is a unified package management application that provides
 a modern GTK3 interface for installing, updating, and managing software
 packages across multiple formats including Flatpak, DEB, and AppImage.
 .
 Key Features:
  * Flatpak package support with automatic repository management
  * DEB package management with APT integration
  * AppImage application integration and management
  * Unified search across all package types
  * Individual and batch package updates
  * Multi-language support (English, Spanish, Portuguese, French, etc.)
  * Modern, intuitive user interface with progress tracking
  * Automatic catalog refresh after operations
 .
 Essora Store simplifies software management on Essora Linux by providing
 a single application to handle all your package management needs, whether
 you're installing system packages, Flatpak applications, or portable
 AppImages.|
